project_descr: The Project aims at providing support for the timely and efficient, free and fair conduct of the presidential election in Zambia by supporting voter education, election day materials and alternative dispute resolution.

donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)
outputs.output_descr: The Project aims at providing support for the timely and efficient, free and fair conduct of the presidential election in Zambia after the demise of the late President H.E. Michael C. Sata on 28 October 2014.
